
Develop environment: Linux + Apache +Mysql

Use PHP framework: Slim ( Beacuse it is very small and can quickly create APIS so I selected it)

The goal: Bulid Restful API used PHP


1.mytask/slim/src/public/open.php

  get user company information



2.mytask/slim/src/public/lib/mysql.php
  connect the database


3.mytask/slim/src/public/index.php
  
  run slim envioment

4. I used Firefox RESTClient test API

  for example: add user

 First set Headers  Content-Type = application/x-www-form-urlencoded;chartset=UTF-8
 
 Sencond set Method = POST URL = http://localhost/open.php/user_add
 Body=user_name=addlei&&birth=2017-02-23&&country=china&&region=beijing&&company=ibm

 Finally SEND.
